{
  "uid": "bmad-memory-overview",
  "title": "BMAD Memory System - Overview",
  "tags": ["bmad", "memory", "overview", "v2"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "version": 4,
  "refresh": "30s",
  "time": {
    "from": "now-30m",
    "to": "now"
  },
  "timepicker": {
    "refresh_intervals": ["10s", "30s", "1m", "5m", "15m", "30m", "1h"]
  },
  "templating": {
    "list": [
      {
        "name": "project",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(bmad_collection_size, project)",
        "query": "label_values(bmad_collection_size, project)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "allValue": ".*",
        "multi": true,
        "regex": "/^(?!all$|shared$).*/",
        "sort": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      },
      {
        "name": "collection",
        "type": "query",
        "datasource": {
          "type": "prometheus",
          "uid": "prometheus"
        },
        "definition": "label_values(bmad_collection_size, collection)",
        "query": "label_values(bmad_collection_size, collection)",
        "includeAll": true,
        "multi": true,
        "sort": 1,
        "current": {
          "text": "All",
          "value": "$__all"
        }
      }
    ]
  },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 100,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 0,
        "w": 24,
        "h": 4
      },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "# BMAD Memory System V2.0 - Overview Dashboard\n\n**Purpose:** Monitor memory system health, usage patterns, and performance across all projects.\n\n**Key Metrics:** Token consumption, trigger activity, collection sizes, capture/retrieval rates\n\n**SLA Targets:** Hooks <500ms | Embeddings <2s | Retrievals <3s | Success Rate >95%\n\n**Documentation:** `/docs/prometheus-queries.md` | **Collections:** code-patterns (HOW), conventions (WHAT), discussions (WHY)"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Total Memories",
      "description": "Total memory entries across all V2.0 collections (code-patterns, conventions, discussions). Yellow >1000, Red >5000. Growth indicates active system usage.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 0,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_collection_size)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Total"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "No data",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "blue"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Context Tokens Injected",
      "description": "Cumulative tokens injected into Claude sessions via SessionStart hook. Represents total memory context provided. Estimated 1500-2500 tokens saved per session retrieval.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 6,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_context_injection_tokens_sum)",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Tokens"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "noValue": "No data",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "green"
              },
              {
                "value": 10000,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 50000,
                "color": "red"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "reduceOptions": {
          "values": false,
          "calcs": ["lastNotNull"]
        },
        "orientation": "auto",
        "textMode": "value_and_name",
        "colorMode": "value",
        "graphMode": "area",
        "justifyMode": "auto"
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "gauge",
      "title": "Success Rate",
      "description": "Memory capture success percentage. Target >95%. Yellow <90%, Red <95%. Low values indicate Qdrant connectivity or hook execution issues.",
      "gridPos": {
        "x": 12,
        "y": 4,
        "w": 6,
        "h": 6
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "sum(bmad_memory_captures_total{status=\"success\"}) / sum(bmad_memory_captures_total) * 100",
          "refId": "A",
          "legendFormat": "Success %"
        }
      ],
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "decimals": 1,
          "noValue": "No data",
          "color": {
            "mode": "thresholds"
          },
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              {
                "value": null,
                "color": "red"
              },
              {
                "value": 90,
                "color": "yellow"
              },
              {
                "value": 95,
                "color": "green"
              }
            ]
          },
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100
        }
      },
      "options": {
        "showThresholdLabels": true,
        "showThresholdMarkers": true
      },
      "datasource": {
        "type": "prometheus",
        "uid": "prometheus"
      }
    },
